title: BABY LILY CARE
description: Take care of Baby Lily in this cute girl game! Bathe her, change her diapers, put her to bed for her nap and prepare some healthy food for the adorable toddler. Lily loves her toys! Play with her and teach her some notes on the piano. She's so talented! Finally, you can select a beautiful costume and dress her up for a party with her friends. They will be impressed!
